body_content.explanation: the level of testosterone (= a hormone that causes the growth of male sexual characteristics) in a person's body:
examples: T levels are actually quite similar over much of the adult life span.

body_content.explanation: in England, a public examination that includes technical subjects, usually taken by students around the age of 17 or 18, or one of the subjects included in this qualification:
examples: Every T Level includes an industry placement with an employer focused on developing practical and technical skills.
The first T level courses started in September 2020.
